title: Fresh Quality Food
typeOfFood: Lacto, International, Raw, Buffet, Fast food, Salad bar, Delivery, Take-out, European, Czech
description: Vegetarian restaurant offers cold, as well as warm dishes, some of which are vegan or can be made vegan, packed with nutrients that you can combine yourself according to your taste and in the quantity that suits you. Uses plant-based proteins such as robi or Goody Foody (a brand), or soy granulate or seitan in goulash dishes or in patties.
